  "texts": [
    "In terms of the environmental score, the following topics are included: (1) air quality;",
    "(2) climate change; (3) ecological and biodiversity impacts; (4) energy; (5) materials and waste; (6) supply chain; (7) water.",
    "Figure 5 provides more detailed proportions and indicators covered by this indicator.",
    "To exclude the influence of other enterprise variables, we also select the following variables as control variables in our empirical model following Hu et al. (2021) and Dong et al. (2022a, b).",
    "(1) Enterprise scale (Size) is measured as the natural logarithm of the total enterprise assets."
  ]
}